Given an array arr of size N, determine whether this array represents an inorder traversal of a BST. 







==============================================================================================================================






class Solution
{
   static int isRepresentingBST(int arr[], int N)
    {
        // code here
        for(int i=0; i<N-1; i++) if(arr[i] >= arr[i+1]) return 0;
        return 1;
    }
}
